{"tid":333774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3賊扮職員入酒店房  23歲女大學生受盡淫辱","createTime":"2017-07-24T06:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T13:38:34.000Z","uid":122,"like":180,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c9f3da650bf50dffd37d06a3b043ffb04ea4d28","tid":333774,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:40:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170724/large/1500830831_1a7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170724%2Flarge%2F1500830831_1a7a.jpg&h=4074fcfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【13:15更新內容】女事主報稱為內地大學生，聲稱遭賊人喝令脫衣摸胸。<br />\n<br />\n一名報稱來自湖北的23歲女大學生，昨日在落馬洲過境後，入住荃灣青山公路135號一間酒店，昨晚11時許，她報稱一名年約20歲至30歲男子敲其房門，她未有理會，其後有兩名男子假扮清潔工人進入其房間後，兩人喝令她拿出財物，之後更露出狼相，著女生脫衣，並向她摸胸非禮，兩人得逞後偕同黨逃去，女事主被劫去約2,300元現金。<br />\n<br />\n女事主其後通知保安協助報警，警員到場調查，案件列作行劫及非禮，交由荃灣警區刑事調查隊第二隊跟進，通緝三名年約20至30歲本地男子。另外，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">由於女生持中國護照，屬過境性質，並不能留港居住，涉嫌逾期居留被捕。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170724/56994726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170724%2F56994726&d=nx8jq1ClmvvomQoMDLd9JQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=f86cae95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170724%2F56994726&h=83b553f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170724/56994726</a>"},{"pid":"366f8556b5b69acdfdd95c94215109badcb27312","tid":333774,"uid":128219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:40:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba504c891f5a0aaa938bd8319faa4702c74232ca","tid":333774,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hk