i\" />"},{"pid":"bf8505c26697bb954a3f3f54c777fd6cadd98703","tid":333774,"uid":1773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:27:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過境可留7 day.報紙佬on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4386b69b6d25051993210a3bf803cf1879f8c13","tid":333774,"uid":18587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:37:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170724/large/1500830831_1a7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170724%2Flarge%2F1500830831_1a7a.jpg&h=4074fcfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【13:15更新內容】女事主報稱為內地大學生，聲稱遭賊人喝令脫衣摸胸。<br />\n<br />\n一名報稱來自湖北的23歲女大學生，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">昨日在落馬洲過境後</span></strong>，入住荃灣青山公路135號一間酒店，昨晚11時許，她報稱一名年約20歲至30歲男子敲其房門，她未有理會，其後有兩名男子假扮清潔工人進入其房間後，兩人喝令她拿出財物，之後更露出狼相，著女生脫衣，並向她摸胸非禮，兩人得逞後偕同黨逃去，女事主被劫去約2,300元現金。<br />\n<br />\n女事主其後通知保安協助報警，警員到場調查，案件列作行劫及非禮，交由荃灣警區刑事調查隊第二隊跟進，通緝三名年約20至30歲本地男子。另外，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">由於女生持中國護照，屬過境性質，並不能留港居住，涉嫌逾期居留被捕。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170724/56994726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170724%2F56994726&d=nx8jq1ClmvvomQoMDLd9JQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=f86cae95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170724%2F56994726&h=83b553f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170724/56994726</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴日先過境 點解咁快就逾期居留？ 咩證要即日返去？</blockquote><br />\n佢只係過境，姐係經香港轉其他交通工具去佢既目的地，所以佢並冇身份逗留</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個係過境，正常佢要有第二程，例如香港機場去第二個國家既機票...，先可以申請過境香港，不過羅湖好多呢d所謂團簽，簽完就可以直接去香港"},{"pid":"57b40ad140dddcf2d7d1b775869dfa62911aea67","tid":333774,"uid":18587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:40:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>過境可留7 day.報紙佬on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係回程先有7 day咩？"},{"pid":"5e0a7d980c1b234b8a6383d15a516c95deaf40f1","tid":333774,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b140012ca9ac0fa1bbf70351948d6f1bbea1481","tid":333774,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:48:20.000Z","msg":"支那人冇一個&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48b2d66efb67d41de260af6c23a931e4f984cce","tid":333774,"uid":122576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:48:58.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7da3ded3fb361dc52a1ae6341a6b174ac892c23","tid":333774,"uid":8748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:49:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170724/large/1500830831_1a7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170724%2Flarge%2F1500830831_1a7a.jpg&h=4074fcfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【13:15更新內容】女事主報稱為內地大學生，聲稱遭賊人喝令脫衣摸胸。<br />\n<br />\n一名報稱來自湖北的23歲女大學生，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">昨日在落馬洲過境後</span></strong>，入住荃灣青山公路135號一間酒店，昨晚11時許，她報稱一名年約20歲至30歲男子敲其房門，她未有理會，其後有兩名男子假扮清潔工人進入其房間後，兩人喝令她拿出財物，之後更露出狼相，著